      <Status>To Do</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43732</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_009_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Arche&gt;え！？　あのヘンテコヘタクソな絵、
